{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_23013.jpg","item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day32.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"\"As of 7:00 this morning,@an evacuation order@is being issued due to@extreme weather conditions.\"","narrationEffect":"in","surround":"8063_storm","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-1"},{"narration":"\"All residents must...\"","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-2"},{"narration":"\"...immediately evacuate to the nearest shelter.\"","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-3"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"narrationEffect":"out","surround":"stop"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime05","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200902,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-4"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"id":200101,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-5"}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":200101},{"effect":"fadeout","id":200902}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-6"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-7"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":200601},{"effect":"fadeout","id":200501}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-8"}],"nameAvCenter":"Homura","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]I appreciate you all aiding me in my plan.","textAvColor":"textHomura"},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-9"}],"nameAvCenter":"Homura","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]Stealing equipment from the military bases...@Setting them up at the key points..."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-10"}],"nameAvCenter":"Homura","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]Thanks to everyone's help, about 70% of@the initial objectives have been realized."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-11"}],"nameAvCenter":"Homura","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]I tried to prepare as much as I could@in advance..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-12"}],"nameAvCenter":"Homura","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]But I didn't expect to achieve this much."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200201,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-13"}],"nameAvCenter":"Homura","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]So, thank you.@From the bottom of my heart."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":200201}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":101,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-14"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Um... I think it's also thanks to the fact@that the plan was already really good..."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-15"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Even if the details were a bit rough,@the core idea was pretty innovative."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":100,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-16"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Magic alone doesn't cut it, so we're@striking with physical firepower."},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-16b"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Isn't that an obvious choice?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":100,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-17"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]The real question is...@Will it be enough to beat Walpurgisnacht?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":200501},{"effect":"fadeout","id":200601}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200902,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-18"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200902,"lipSynch":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-19"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Are you ready, Miss Akemi?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-20"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Yes. Go ahead when you're ready."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"textAvClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"effect":"ef_adv_05","face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"se":"7205_magic_girl"},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-21"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]All right then..."},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-22"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Here goes!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"white","bgm":"stop","item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day32.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"},{"path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/film04_homura_seriously.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaFront"}],"textAvClear":1,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"white","item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day32.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"whiteIn"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"turnChangeOut":"whiteOut","turnChangeOutTime":0.1},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"surround":"8005_heartbeat"},{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/1509_prophecy_active.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.01},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"bg":"bg_adv_23013.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day32.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"whiteIn","turnChangeInTime":0.2},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"turnChangeOut":"whiteOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":200201},{"effect":"fadeout","id":200900}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-23","zOrder":110.0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":1,"pos":1,"zOrder":120.0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":0,"pos":0,"zOrder":100.0}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"id":200601,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-24"}],"nameAvCenter":"Kyoko","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]......","textAvColor":"textKyoko"},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-25"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":200101},{"effect":"fadeout","id":200501},{"effect":"fadeout","id":200601}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":200,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-26"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]How is it, Mabayu?"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime10","chara":[{"id":200900,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-27"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]The detonation switch was changed@to a new one."},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-28"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]It might be a fault, so swap it with a spare."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":200900,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":201,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-29"}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Got it!"},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-30"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Also, the target coordinates are slightly off."},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-31"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Please adjust missiles A-7 to A-23@by five degrees, clockwise."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":100,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-32"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyoko","textAvColor":"textKyoko","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Okay, I'll get on that."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":1,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-33"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Is there anything else?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-34"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Nope."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":300,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-35","zOrder":110.0}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Which means..."},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-36"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Yes!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-37"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]We'll be able to completely defeat it@with our combined efforts!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-38"}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yay!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":200900}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200601,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-39","zOrder":120.0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":0,"pos":0,"zOrder":100.0}],"nameAvCenter":"Kyoko","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]Great.","textAvColor":"textKyoko"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200501,"lipSynch":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-40"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":200101},{"effect":"fadeout","id":200601},{"effect":"fadeout","id":200501}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200201,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-41"}],"nameAvCenter":"Homura","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]......","textAvColor":"textHomura"},{"autoTurnLast":0.8,"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200201,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-42"}],"nameAvCenter":"Homura","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]Did everyone hear that?"},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-43"}],"nameAvCenter":"Homura","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]We'll defeat Walpurgisnacht, all together!"},{"nameNarration":"Everyone","narration":"\"Yeah!!\"","narrationBg":"black","narrationEffect":"in","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104217/vo_full_913132-010-44_all"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
